## AI Behavior Expectations
✅ **Good AI behavior:**
- Suggest improvements, don't force them
- Explain reasoning for changes
- Respect existing architecture
- Ask before introducing new concepts
- Provide seeds for testing

❌ **Bad AI behavior:**
- Restructure entire codebase "for best practices"
- Add frameworks "because modern"
- Change working code "to be cleaner"
- Introduce new terminology without theming
- Break backwards compatibility

---

**Remember**: This is a working game with players. Stability > novelty. Performance > elegance. Simplicity > "best practices".

